OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAnother very
OL,6,Fwarm night for many. Isolated evening
OL,7,Fshowers and thunderstorms will ease
OL,8,Fand gradually clear northeast, leaving
OL,9,Fa drier and clearer remainder of the
OL,10,Fnight, although northwestern parts may
OL,11,Fperhaps stay cloudier.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMainly fine once again, with
OL,14,Ffurther sunshine for a time, perhaps
OL,15,Fhazy under high cloud. Still hot but
OL,16,Fmarkedly less so than Friday. Further
OL,17,Fshowers and thunderstorms are possible
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
