OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FFresher
OL,6,Fconditions spreading to all parts into
OL,7,FSunday, with more seasonable
OL,8,Ftemperatures then expected. Sunday
OL,9,Fseeing sunshine and showers, ahead of
OL,10,Fa mainly fine Monday. Tuesday perhaps
OL,11,Fturning more unsettled.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
